quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  35,41,"Nokorε sε Onyankopͻn na Okuta ͻsoro ne asaase mu sεdeε emfiri (netebea) hͻ. Nasε efiri hͻ a, obiara nnihͻ a obetumi asͻ mu ka Neho. Nokorε sε Ɔne Ntoboaseε Hene, Ɔne Bͻnefakyε Wura"
  35,42,"Wͻ’de Nyankopͻn dii wͻn nsedie akεseε no sε: “Sε kͻkͻbͻfoͻ bi baa wͻn hͻ a anka wͻ’bεyε ateneneefoͻ akyεn ͻman biara. Nanso ͻkͻkͻbͻni baa wͻn hͻ no wͻn annya nkͻsoͻ biara na mmom dwanee (na wͻ’dwanee nokorε no)"
  35,43,"Yεε akεsesεm wͻ asaase no so bͻͻ pͻ bͻne; na pͻ bͻne no, enya obiara na mmom deε ͻbͻͻ (pͻ bͻne no ara na εbenya) no. Enti deε wͻ’retwεn ara ne (asotwee) a εtoo tetefoͻ no (sεso)? Wonya nsesaeε wͻ Onyankopͻn kwan no mu, na wonhunu nsakraeε nso wͻ kwan a Onyankopͻn atwa ato hͻ no so"
  35,44,"Enti wͻ’nntu kwan wͻ asaase no so nhwε sεdeε wͻn a wͻ’dii wͻn anim kan no awieε si wieε? Na wͻn ho yε den sen wͻn wͻ tumi mu. Onyankopᴐn deε biribiara nnihͻ a etumi bu fa ne so wͻ soro anaasε asaase so. Nokorε sε Ɔne Onimdefoͻ, Ɔne Otumfoᴐ"
  35,45,"Sε anka Onyankopͻn retwe nnipa aso (wiase ha) wͻ dwuma a wͻn adie ho a, anka εnka abͻdeε biara wͻ asase no so, na mmom Ɔma wͻn berε dekosi εberε a yahyε ato hͻ no. Enti sε wͻn berε no so a, εneε nokorε sε Onyankopͻn deε Ohu Nenkoa no (nyinaa)"
  36,1,Yaa siin
  36,2,Nyankopͻn de Qur’aan a Nyansa ne adwen ahyε mu mma no di nse sε
  36,3,"(Nkͻmhyεni), nokorε sε woka Asomafoͻ no ho"
  36,4,(Na wonam) ͻkwan tenenee no so
  36,5,"(Qur’aan) yε Adiyisεm a efri Otumfoͻ, Mͻborͻhunufoͻ Hene no hͻ"
  36,6,"Sεdeε wode bεbͻ amanfoͻ a yammͻ wͻn agyanom kͻkͻ no a, enti wͻn werε afri (wͻn ho) no kͻkͻ"
  36,7,"Ampa sε, asεm no mu nokorε atia wͻn mu (nnipa) pii, efirisε wͻ’nnye nni"
  36,8,"Nokorε sε, Yε’de dadewεmfoͻ agu wͻn kͻn mu abεpem wͻn abͻdwe, enti wͻn ti apagya hwε soro (a wͻ’ntumi nnsi wͻn tri aseε)"
  36,9,"Yε’de εban nso asi wͻn anim, εna εban san wͻ wͻn akyi εna Y’akata wͻn soͻ, enti wͻn nhunu hwee"
  36,10,"Sε wobͻ wͻn kͻkͻ o, anaasε w’ammͻ wͻn kͻkͻ o, ԑyε asεm korͻ ma wͻn sԑ wͻ’nnye nni"
  36,11,"Nea εsεsε wobͻ no kͻkͻ ne obi a odi Afutusεm (Qur’aan) no akyi, na osuro Ahummͻborͻ Hene no wͻ kokoa mu. (Nkͻmhyεni), Fa bͻnefakyε ne Animuonyam akatua kεseε no ho bͻhyԑ ma (saa nipa) no"
  36,12,"Nokorε sε, Yεn na Yenyane awufoͻ no, na Yε’twerε deε (adasamma ayε) de ato (wͻn) anim ne (faako a) wͻn anamͻn (anante akͻduru biara), na Y’asese biribiara wͻ Nwoma pefee no mu"
  36,13,"Fa kuro (Antiok) so foͻ no yε mfatoho ma wͻn, εberε a Asomafoͻ no baa wͻn hͻ no"
  36,14,"Ɛberε a Yε’somaa (Asomafoͻ) mmienu kᴐᴐ wͻn hͻ no, wͻ’annye wͻn anni, enti Yε’de deε ͻtͻso mmiεnsa bεfoaa wͻn so; na wͻ’ka kyerεε (kuro no mu foͻ no) sε: “Nokorε sε, yε’yε moasomafoͻ’’"
  36,15,"(Antiokfoͻ no) kaa sε: ”Moyε nnipa tesε yεn ara. Ahummͻborͻ Hene no nsianee hwee (maa mo), mo saa (nkorͻfoͻ yi) moyε nkontompofoͻ”"
  36,16,"(Asomafoͻ no) kaa sε: “Ye’Wura Nyankopͻn Nim yie sε, nokorε, yε’yε Asomafoͻ ma mo"
  36,17,"Y’adwuma ara nesε, yεbεbͻ (Asεm no ho) dawuro akyerεkyerε mu"
  36,18,"(Antiokfoͻ no) kaa sε: ‘’Yehunu sε moyε mmusuo ma yεn, enti sε moanyae (monsεm no ka) a, yεbesi mo aboͻ, na yεde asotwee a εyε ya paa a efri yεn hͻ atwe moaso"
  36,19,"(Asomafoͻ no) kaa sε: “Mommusuo no fri mo ara mohͻ, sε anka moredwen a. Daabi, moyε nnipa nsεmmͻnedifoͻ"
  36,20,"Ɔbarima bi (Habiib Najaar) de ahoͻherε fri kuro no akyirikyiri baabi bae bεkaa sε: “Menkorͻfoͻ, moni Asomafoͻ no akyi"
  36,21,"Moni wͻn a wͻ’mmisa mo (nsεmpa a wͻ’reka kyerε mo) no ho akatua no akyi, efrisε wͻ’yε ateneneefoͻ"
  36,22,"Ԑdeεn nti na εnsεsε mesom (Nyankopͻn) no a Ɔbͻͻ me, na Nehͻ na mobεsan akͻ"
  36,23,"Menfri N’akyi mfa anyame (foforͻ nsom wͻn wͻ aberε a) sε Ahummͻborͻ Hene Nyankopͻn pε me bͻne anaa ͻhaw bi a, (anyame no) ntwitwagyeε ho mma me mfasoͻ biara, na wͻ’nntumi nnye me nso"
  36,24,"(Sε meyε saa a), εneε na nokorε sε, mewͻ ͻyera pefee paa mu"
  36,25,Nokorε sε m’agye mo Wura Nyankopͻn no adi enti montie me”
  36,26,"Yε’ka kyerεε no sε: ”Wura Soro Aheman no mu. (Habiib) kaa sε: “Sε anka menkorͻfoͻ no nim"
  36,27,"Sεdeε me Wura Nyankopͻn de me bͻne akyε me, na Ɔde me aka animuonyamfoͻ no ho a”"